<br>
Snot-Nosed Twit:Well, I believe that if I jump off of the top of the Empire State Building, I will miss the pavement and begin to fly.<br>
<br>
Me: With all due respect, that's preposterous.  Gravity suggests... blah blah blah... and you'll simply go *Splat*.<br>
<br>
SNT: *Snorts indignantly* Well, who are <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>you</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> to tell me what to believe!? I have every right to have an opinion too, ya know.  <br>
<br>
